criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All physicians (residents and experts) of the Surgical Division at Tel Aviv Sourasky
             Medical Center.

          -  All medical students studying at the Sackler Faculty of Medicine, Tel Aviv University,
             and attending a surgery round at the Surgical Division at Tel Aviv Sourasky Medical
             Center.

          -  Patients (and/or family members) in the Surgical Division at Tel Aviv Sourasky Medical
             Center following their surgery.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  The research will not include children and/or judgment-impaired patients;

          -  population not met by inclusion criteria;

          -  non-Hebrew speaking patients;

          -  ventilated patients;

          -  patients in surgical intensive care;

          -  patients medically defined as suffering from clouding of conscious or delirium;

          -  subjects who decided to stop their participation in the study.
